Vallum is a hack-proof wallet built on Solana, the next generation of self-custody hot wallets. 

Engineered for ultimate security, Vallum leverages Solanas’s high speed, low cost blockchain to deliver a seamless, user-controlled crypto experience. 

With real-time threat detection, it safeguards your assets from hacks and unauthorised access. 

Designed for both beginners and experts, Vallum offers intuitive interface, instant transactions, and full ownership of your private keys.
